},{"role":"present_2mp","form":"تَلِجُونَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_2fp","form":"تَلِجْنَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"p"},{"role":"present_3ms","form":"يَلِج","in_corpus":true,"count":5,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_3fs","form":"تَلِج","in_corpus":true,"count":1,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"present_3md","form":"يَلِجا","in_corpus":true,"count":2,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3md","form":"يَلِجانِ","in_corpus":true,"count":1,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3fd","form":"تَلِجا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3fd","form":"تَلِجانِ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3mp","form":"يَلِجُوا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_3mp","form":"يَلِجُونَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_3fp","form":"يَلِجْنَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"p"},{"role":"present_1mp","form":"نَلِج","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_1ms","form":"أَلِج","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"past_1ms","form":"وَلَجْتُ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"past_1mp","form":"وَلَجْنا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"p"}],"frequency_in_corpus":11,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n42331"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%88%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%AC%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n42331","headword_ar":"وَلَجَ","root":"wlj","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaliju","text_ar":"يَلِجُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wuluwjN","text_ar":"وُلُوجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lijapN","text_ar":"لِجَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_it~alaja","text_ar":"اـِتَّلَجَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"twl~j","text_ar":"تولّج","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (L;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, entered."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"walaja Albayota","text_ar":"وَلَجَ البَيْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"At~ljh","text_ar":"اتّلجه","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"twl~jhu","text_ar":"تولّجهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He entered the house."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"walaja Al$~aYo'u fiY gayrihi","text_ar":"وَلَجَ الشَّىْءُ فِى غَيرِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The thing entered into another thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) As is said in the S and L, Sb says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"walaja","text_ar":"وَلَجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"has for its inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wuluwjN","text_ar":"وُلُوجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is of one of the measures of the inf. ns. of intrans. verbs, because the meaning [of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"walajotu Albayota","text_ar":"وَلَجْتُ البَيْتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"walajotu fiyhi","text_ar":"وَلَجْتُ فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and it is said in the M, that Sb holds the intermediate particle to be dropped: but Mohammad Ibn-Yezeed holds the verb to be trans. without an intermediate particle. MF observes, that Sb's words appear to make"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wlj","text_ar":"ولج"},{"kind":"text","text":"a trans. verb, which no one asserts it to be: that if he mean that it has as its complement a noun in the acc. case as an adverbial noun of place, it is like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daxalotu","text_ar":"دَخَلْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and other intrans. verbs: but if he mean that it governs a simple objective complement, like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Darabotu zayodFA","text_ar":"ضَرَبْتُ زَيْدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", his opinion is not correct. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}